name: Django-Scapy
body:
### Welcome to Django-Scapy.
Django-Scapy is a Web Based Network Protocol Analyzer using [Scapy3K](https://github.com/phaethon/scapy) and [Django](https://github.com/django/django). Goal is to build a web based Wireshark like Network Protocol Analyzer.

### Authors and Contributors
Author: @erikdewildt
If you want to help, contact me!
